cff-version: 1.2.0
title: "Migiwa: A Minimal Human-Contact Review Kernel for AI Systems"
message: "If you use or cite Migiwa, please cite this repository and its release version."
type: software
version: "0.1.0"
date-released: "2026-06-17"
authors:
  - name: "Migiwa Project contributors"
repository-code: "https://github.com/ty-mmh/migiwa"
url: "https://github.com/ty-mmh/migiwa"
license: "CC-BY-4.0 AND MIT"
abstract: >
  Migiwa is a minimal human-contact review kernel for AI systems. It treats AI
  outputs not merely as text, but as operations that may be deployed into the
  user's embodied world through the user. It reviews contact pressure before AI
  outputs enter human workflows, relationships, institutions, and decisions.
keywords:
  - human-AI interaction
  - AI evaluation
  - contact pressure
  - AI deployment
  - responsible AI
  - AI governance
  - HCI
  - CSCW
  - LLM evaluation
